Interface FieldValuePairQueryNode<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FieldableNode, QueryNode, ValueQueryNode<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface FieldValuePairQueryNode<T>
extends FieldableNode, ValueQueryNode<T>
